xyz.kotlout.kotlout.model.experiment

Class Post

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.kotlout.kotlout.model.experiment.Post

  • public class Post
extends java.lang.Object
    A Post is a class representing a question or reply posted to an experiment's discussion forum. is a simple POJO class so that it may be serialized onto firebase.

        Parameters:
        postId - Document ID in firebase
        poster - UUID of User who created this post
        parent - UUID of the post this is a reply to, must be in the same collection,if null this is top-level.
        text - Body of the post
        timestamp - the timestamp
